{"tid":2417094,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"陳雲：我隨時被控告入獄或被控告破產的。","createTime":"2021-02-21T14:49:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-22T03:36:44.000Z","uid":228143,"like":4,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a2458e3e97f635b3d69037cadbed6bbfb7c6183a","tid":2417094,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T14:49:17.000Z","msg":"陳雲：這個短片，篤爆政府的疫情醜聞！如果傳閱量夠多，足以停止政府封樓及廣泛檢測，我就要看香港人是否支持正義，還是認輸、認命！<br />\n<br />\n病毒化驗公司超負荷懷疑集體亂龍，出現假陽性！犧牲科學標準，政府亂封樓封區擴大檢測。借疫情奴役人民！<br />\n<br />\n這是非常嚴峻的獨家新聞分析！我隨時被控告入獄或被控告破產的。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/8fo9Vo0offE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F8fo9Vo0offE&d=nAM79WGQOJ1S2Ssbv1FDY13VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=712679be\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/8fo9Vo0offE</a><br />\n<br />\n邊個話佢唔屌政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n得佢敢屌真係唔驚國安法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8cac6faa483f3fb8946a4c90b71888d0ed2bbfe","tid":2417094,"uid":186431,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T14:52:13.000Z","msg":"似入青山多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohyes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"228310ccd2d89cdc9ee468991c9ec2e0ffd718a3","tid":2417094,"uid":197783,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T14:55:08.000Z","msg":"屌你老母臭閪，冇人想見到依隻禿頭騙子呀。<br />\n<br />\n收鳩皮啦，<br />\n<br />\n全世界都冇人講肺炎架喇，你條柒頭皮收撚埋啦。<br />\n<br />\n落下街睇下幾撚多人食飯啦。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母！！"},{"pid":"8c589386654834fb39a19da39a37153b532129b3","tid":2417094,"uid":191790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T15:04:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dbcba7df91d6d9f046d8da0b8b837d79f8508dec","tid":2417094,"uid":75390,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T15:15:02.000Z","msg":"陳雲點會破產呀 佢搵咁多錢<br